Package ec.co.ant

Class GlobalUpdateRule

java.lang.Object
ec.co.ant.GlobalUpdateRule
All Implemented Interfaces:
UpdateRule, Setup, Serializable
public class GlobalUpdateRule extends Object implements UpdateRule
A "global" pheromone update rule in the style of Ant Colony System. Either the best ant of the run (GLOBAL_BEST) or best of the generation (ITERATION_BEST) is chosen according to base.best-strategy and used to deposit pheromones.
Author:
Eric O. Scott
